      ***************************************************************           
      *  THIS PROGRAM IS CALLED FROM BATCH PROGRAMS TO PASS MESSAGES            
      *  TO NETCOOL.  ISKUT004 IS THE CICS VERSION OF THIS PROGRAM.             
      *--------------------------------------------------------------           
      *  JJR  12/29/1999  CREATED.                                              
      *  JJR  07/06/2000  CHANGED TO USE MQSERIES INSTEAD OF GDG FILES          
      *                   THAT ARE SENT VIA FTP TO NETCOOL.                     
      *                   PUT MOST OF THE CODE INTO COPYBOOKS SO CHANGES        
      *                   FOR BATCH AND CICS ARE DONE ONLY ONCE.                
      *  JJR  03/09/2001  CHANGED TO USE MQSERIES ROUTINE TO GET                
      *                   REASON DESCRIPTIONS.                                  
      ***************************************************************           
                                                                                
       DATA DIVISION.                                                           
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.                                                 
                                                                                
           COPY ISWS002.                                                        
           COPY ISWS004.                                                        
           COPY ISPD004.                                                        
           COPY ISPD002.                                                        
                                                                                
                                                                                
       1002-GET-JOB-INFO.                                                       
                                                                                
           CALL PC-GETJOBNM USING PV-JOB-DATA.                                  
           IF PV-JOB-NAME (1:3) = 'TKM'                                         
               SET PV-TEST-ENVIRONMENT TO TRUE                                  
           ELSE                                                                 
               SET PV-PROD-ENVIRONMENT TO TRUE                                  
           END-IF.                                                              
